            <fullName>Manage_Appointment_179ak000002oR0f</fullName>
            <description>Use this action to cancel or reschedule a confirmed booking. Required inputs are the patient&apos;s appointment number (e.g. SA-0017) and patientLookupEmail as a plain email string only (e.g. priya.sharma@example.com). patientLookupEmail MUST be a simple string literal—never a JSON object and never include recipientId, subject, body, to, or cc. Do not pass Salesforce record Ids. You must check the 24-hour guardrail rule (via the Apex logic) before proceeding. Do not use this for general inquiries.</description>
            <developerName>Manage_Appointment_179ak000002oR0f</developerName>
            <invocationTarget>OncoAppointmentManager</invocationTarget>
            <invocationTargetType>apex</invocationTargetType>
            <isConfirmationRequired>false</isConfirmationRequired>
            <isIncludeInProgressIndicator>true</isIncludeInProgressIndicator>
