        <localActions>
            <fullName>Onco_Search_Specialties_Nav_179ak000002oR1e</fullName>
            <description>Lists oncology specialty programs / departments. ALWAYS call this tool when the user asks any of: &quot;what specialties / departments do you offer&quot;, &quot;what kinds of cancer care do you have&quot;, &quot;do you have a paediatric / gynae / radiation / surgical / medical oncology department&quot;, &quot;list your oncology programs&quot;, &quot;browse by department&quot;, or before department-first booking. Do not answer these from memory—run this action. Returns patient-safe names in specialtiesText and CareSpecialty Ids in plannerReferenceText for Get Available Appointment Slots (department-first) and follow-on tools.</description>
